        <abstract> 
<p>Has read sheets of AG’s third <hi rend="italic">Atlantic Monthly</hi> article [Oct 1860] and praises it and AG’s other reviews and articles highly.</p> 
            <p>Is surprised at the inability of others to grasp the meaning of natural selection.</p> 
<p>Has been testing the sensitivity of <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>, which he finds remarkable.</p> 
            <p>Asks if AG will be able to make some observations on orchids for him.</p>
        </abstract>
